---
// src/pages/index.astro
import DocsLayout from '../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout title="Welcome to ROːBIT Archive" isDocs={false}>
	<section class="relative py-16 px-8 mb-16 overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] bg-gradient-to-br from-zinc-900 via-zinc-800 to-black text-white shadow-2xl">
		<div class="relative z-10">
		<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black mb-6 leading-[1.1]">
			Korea's First, <br/>
			<span class="text-blue-500">Global Leader in Robotics.</span>
			<!-- 슬로건은 재민이형이 말해주는 내용으로 수정 필요. 지금은 임의로 추가함.-->
		</h2>
		<p class="text-zinc-400 max-w-xl mb-10 text-lg leading-relaxed">
			광운대학교 로봇게임단 로빛의 20여 년간의 기술 자산과 대회 기록을 체계적으로 보존하는 공식 아카이브입니다.
		</p>
		<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
			<a href="/overview/welcome" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold transition-all transform hover:scale-105">
			시작하기
			</a>
			<a href="https://github.com/team-robit" target="_blank" class="bg-zinc-800/50 backdrop-blur-md border border-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold transition-all">
			GitHub 저장소
			</a>
		</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
		<a href="/robots/robot-list" class="group p-8 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 rounded-3xl hover:border-blue-500/50 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:hover:bg-zinc-900/50 transition-all">
		<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">🤖</div>
		<h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">Our Robots</h3>
		<p class="text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
			로빛의 역대 레스큐, 재난 대응 로봇들의 사양과 설계 문서를 확인하세요.
		</p>
		</a>

		<a href="/contest/awards" class="group p-8 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 rounded-3xl hover:border-orange-500/50 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:hover:bg-zinc-900/50 transition-all">
		<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 dark:bg-orange-900/30 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">🏆</div>
		<h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">Achievements</h3>
		<p class="text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
			국내외 로봇 대회 수상 실적과 주요 경기 리포트를 열람할 수 있습니다.
		</p>
		</a>

		<a href="/members/current" class="group p-8 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 rounded-3xl hover:border-emerald-500/50 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:hover:bg-zinc-900/50 transition-all">
		<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-100 dark:bg-emerald-900/30 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">👥</div>
		<h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">People</h3>
		<p class="text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
			로빛을 빛낸 역대 단원들과 현재 활동 중인 19, 20기 지능팀 정보를 확인하세요.
		</p>
		</a>
	</div>
</DocsLayout>